<p class="courseblockdesc">
Concentration on developing compositional and orchestration/arranging skills in various jazz and commercial styles. Course Information: Prerequisite(s): Grade of C or better in <a href="/search/?P=MUS%20120" title="MUS 120" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MUS 120');">MUS 120</a> and Grade of C or better in <a href="/search/?P=MUS%20221" title="MUS 221" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MUS 221');">MUS 221</a>; and junior standing or above; or approval of the department. Majors may have only one D in 300-level courses.<br/>
