8" title="MUS 118" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MUS 118');">MUS 118</a> A grade of C or above in any Music Literature course (<a href="/search/?P=MUS%20113" title="MUS 113" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MUS 113');">MUS 113</a>, <a href="/search/?P=MUS%20114" title="MUS 114" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MUS 114');">114</a>, <a href="/search/?P=MUS%20115" title="MUS 115" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MUS 115');">115</a>, <a href="/search/?P=MUS%20117" title="MUS 117" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MUS 117');">117</a>, <a href="/search/?P=MUS%20118" title="MUS 118" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MUS 118');">118</a>, <a href="/search/?P=MUS%20127" title="MUS 127" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MUS 127');">127</a>, <a href="/search/?P=MUS%20119" title="MUS 119" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MUS 119');">119</a>, <a href="/search/?P=MUS%20240" title="MUS 240" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MUS 240');">240</a>.<br/>
