<p class="courseblockdesc">
Building on Acting Fundamentals (<a href="/search/?P=THTR%20145" title="THTR 145" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'THTR 145');">THTR 145</a>), students expand knowledge of theatre ideas/vocabulary and develop acting skill through readings, scene work, audition practices, and attendance at theatre productions in Chicago and UIC. Course Information: Field trips required at a nominal fee. Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=THTR%20145" title="THTR 145" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'THTR 145');">THTR 145</a> <a href="/search/?P=THTR%20145" title="THTR 145" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'THTR 145');">THTR 145</a> or consent of the instructor.<br/>
